<chapter id="core_logging_resource">
	<title>Resources</title>
	<para>
		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem>
				<para>
					Download
				</para>
				<para>
					Download hsqldb.zip containing test DB and anyframe-sample-logging.zip file containing example code
						in the following and extract those files.
						And execute start.cmd (or start.sh) file under hsqldb folder
						and start the test DB.					
					<itemizedlist>
						<listitem>
							<para>Maven-based run</para>
							<para>
								After moving to extracted folder in the command window,
								execute command named 'mvn compile exec:java -Dexec.mainClass=...'
								and check the execution result.
								Refer to JavaDoc of Main class in each Eclipse project.							
							</para>
						</listitem>
						<listitem>
							<para>Eclipse-based run</para>
							<para>
										After importing extracted project on Eclipse,
									select Main.java under anyframe/sample/logging in src/main/java,
									and click mouse right button and click on Run As > Java Application on the context menu. Check the execution result.							
							</para>
						</listitem>									
					</itemizedlist>
				</para>
